     D PZAlignOk       S              1A
     D PZField         S             16A
     D PZADec          S              1P 0
     D PZADig          S              2P 0
     D PPrct           S              5A

     D Idx             S              3P 0
     D WIdx            S              3P 0
      ** Index for arrays of error message ids etc

